<% provide(:title, "FlowFree") %>

<div class="row">
  <div class="large-12 columns center-iframe">
    <div id="googft-mapCanvas"></div>
    <hr>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="large-4 columns">
    <%= image_tag("http://placehold.it/400x300&text=[img]") %>
  </div>
  <div class="large-8 columns">
    <h4>This is a content section.</h4>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="large-6 columns">
          <p>Bacon ipsum dolor sit amet nulla ham qui sint exercitation eiusmod commodo, chuck duis velit. Aute in reprehenderit, dolore aliqua non est magna in labore pig pork biltong. Eiusmod swine spare ribs reprehenderit culpa. Boudin aliqua adipisicing rump corned beef.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="large-6 columns">
          <div id='state-drop-dwn'>
            <%= form_tag rivers_by_state_path do %>
              <%= select_tag :state, options_for_select(us_states), :prompt => 'Select A State' %>
              <%= submit_tag "Go!" %>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="large-8 columns">
    <h4>This is a content section.</h4>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="large-6 columns">
           <%= form_tag rivers_by_name_path do %>
              <%= text_field_tag :search, params[:search] %>
              <%= submit_tag "Search" %>
           <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class="large-6 columns">
          <p>Pork drumstick turkey fugiat. Tri-tip elit turducken pork chop in. Swine short ribs meatball irure bacon nulla pork belly cupidatat meatloaf cow. Nulla corned beef sunt ball tip, qui bresaola enim jowl. Capicola short ribs minim salami nulla nostrud pastrami.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
  </div>
  <div class="large-4 columns">
    <%= image_tag("http://placehold.it/400x300&text=[img]") %>
  </div>
</div>

